# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

---

## [v1.0.0] – 2024-04-29

🎉 **Initial Release**

### Features:
- Drag-and-drop **block canvas** to structure QR data visually
- Support for:
  - Text
  - Tabs (`\t`)
  - Returns (`\r`)
- **Live QR preview**
- **Preset manager**: save/load/delete layouts to/from browser storage
- Option to **copy QR image** directly to clipboard (as PNG)
- **Trash dropzone** for deleting blocks
- Responsive layout optimized for desktop

### Known Limitations:
- ⚠️ **Touch input (mobile) support is limited** – drag-and-drop and editing require desktop use
- ⚠️ Clipboard image copy may not work in non-HTTPS environments or unsupported browsers
- 📱 Mobile usability improvements and long-press support planned in future updates

---
